As I walked back into my house to inform my husband Paul of the awful news, I saw him throwing it back to the song 💞four💞in💞her💕... absolutely repulsive behavior. I tried to snap him out of it but he kept acting like a robot. The dining table didn’t like the fact that I wanted him to stop so it launched himself at me knocking me to the floor causing me to pass out. When I woke up I saw that I had a concussion. As I was driving my self to the hospital with a concussion the car started floating in the air. All of the government controlled birds came at me and started to chirp “TRUMP 2020 TRUMP 2020” they then preceded to attack my car as it was floating. I was then mortified and deleted the app. So if any of you trump supports, like me, are considering to download the app so show our love and support, please do not unless you want to be eaten alive by a cicada 🧚‍♀️ 🧚‍♀️ 🧚‍♂️ 🧚‍♀️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♀️🧚‍♀️
